Abdomen (
Figs 5–7
) 2.2–2.4 mm long. Tergites I–III, VIII without shagreen. Hook row 153–204 µm long, with 44–50 spines. Tergites III–V on posterior margin with transverse band of strong dark spines distributed in 2–4 rows (tergite III with 47–62 spines, IV with 50–70 spines, V with 51–75 spines), tergite VI with weaker spines. Tergite IV with pair of anterolateral patches of shagreen (
